{"title":"大连二首","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登鸡冠山日俄旧战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅顺口美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅顺口温柔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅顺口不冻的良港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向四海五洲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年，北极熊咬它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东瀛狼来争肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆发了那场熊狼斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊也伤亡，狼也伤亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"败者是贼，胜者是寇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疼痛百年的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中国的伤口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事不堪回首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事必须回首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆耻辱，为了争光荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头看，为了向前走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡冠山引颈长鸣吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们闻鸡起舞，长剑在手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜脚印甬路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为纪念大连建市一百周年，大连人用一千英模脚印，在星海广场铸出铜甬路，通向海边掀开的大书……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一千精英脚印制模，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇铸出一条铜的甬路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺在星海广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向那本打开的书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天，日光在上面飞渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，星光在上面跳舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海浪像脚步声声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在流光的征途……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走在铜脚印甬路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禁不住心潮起伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，来路已经留在身后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该怎样走好新的一步？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}